xtc.lang.blink.agent

Interface AgentCommandOptions

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DebugeeJVM

    public interface AgentCommandOptions
    The Blink Agent's constant values visible to the Blink through the Java component debugger. The constant here should be consistent with the options.h file.
